Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《盲点》前情回顾\N{\fs14\b0}Previously on "Blindspot"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特助理局长失踪了  推测已死亡\N{\fs14\b0}Assistant Director Carter is missing, presumed dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14\b0}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们或许应该谈谈昨晚的事\N{\fs14\b0}We should probably talk about last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住的那条街  街尾有个公园\N{\fs14\b0}There's a park at the end of my street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们十点在那儿见\N{\fs14\b0}Meet me there at 10:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们讨论了和威勒探员划清界限的问题\N{\fs14\b0}We discussed setting clearer boundaries with Agent Weller.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展如何\N{\fs14\b0}How's that been going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\fs14\b0}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怕你  也确实该怕\N{\fs14\b0}They're scared of you... and they should be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有任务要交给你\N{\fs14\b0}I have missions for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得按我的方式来\N{\fs14\b0}We do this on my terms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些就是你的方式\N{\fs14\b0}These are your terms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是你的计划\N{\fs14\b0}This is all your plan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实施的时候到了\N{\fs14\b0}And it's time to get started.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要干什么\N{\fs14\b0}So what now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs14\b0}Now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你第一个任务\N{\fs14\b0}your first mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs14\b0}What is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梅菲尔那支钢笔的复制品\N{\fs14\b0}It's an exact replica of Mayfair's pen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道梅菲尔的笔是什么样子\N{\fs14\b0}How do you know what Mayfair's pen looks like?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们安装了摄像头了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you have cameras in there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我们...自有办法\N{\fs14\b0}No, we... we have another way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你把她的笔掉包\N{\fs14\b0}I need you to swap 'em{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来交给我\N{\fs14\b0}and bring me hers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们抹去了我的记忆\N{\fs14\b0}So you wipe my memory,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我全身纹了纹身\N{\fs14\b0}you tattoo my entire body,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把我送进联调局\N{\fs14\b0}and then you send me to the FBI{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了让我偷一支笔\N{\fs14\b0}so I can steal a pen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\b0}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你还是一点没变啊\N{\fs14\b0}You're still-- you're still you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么\N{\fs14\b0}What is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监听器  追踪器\N{\fs14\b0}A bug? A tracker?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会背叛我的队友\N{\fs14\b0}Because I won't betray my team.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是背叛  就是一支笔而已\N{\fs14\b0}It's not a betrayal, it's a pen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的笔\N{\fs14\b0}A regular pen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道不是你\N{\fs14\b0}How do I know that you weren't{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿枪逼着我说出视频里那番话\N{\fs14\b0}holding a gun to my head during that video?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没拿枪指着你过\N{\fs14\b0}I've never pointed a gun at you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么傻\N{\fs14\b0}I know better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真这么以为  你就不会来了\N{\fs14\b0}And if you really thought that, you wouldn't be here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会把你的队友带来\N{\fs14\b0}You'd have sent your team.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你没有\N{\fs14\b0}But you didn't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为冥冥之中\N{\fs14\b0}because, somehow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道自己不属于他们中的一员\N{\fs14\b0}you know that you're not one of them,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是他们团队里的一颗齿轮而已\N{\fs14\b0}that you're just a cog in their machine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有用的时候就百般拉拢\N{\fs14\b0}Welcome while useful,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去价值了就立马抛弃\N{\fs14\b0}disposable the second you're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯进我安全屋的那个男人是怎么回事\N{\fs14\b0}What about the man at my safe house...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有胡子的那个\N{\fs14\b0}with the beard?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你们的人吗\N{\fs14\b0}Was he with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们一起的吗\N{\fs14\b0}With us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那支笔拿来给我\N{\fs14\b0}Bring me that pen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就告诉你更多答案\N{\fs14\b0}and I'll give you more answers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他起来吃的时候都被果酱泡软了\N{\fs14\b0}It's gonna get soggy by the time he eats it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得先把两片都涂上花生酱\N{\fs14\b0}You got to put peanut butter on both sides first{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果酱夹在中间\N{\fs14\b0}and jelly in the middle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  没看出来你还是果酱三明治大师\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, sorry, I had no idea you were such an expert on PB&J.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是\N{\fs14\b0}Well, that I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我给你示范一下吗\N{\fs14\b0}So... do you want me to show you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-您请  -好的\N{\fs14\b0}- By all means. - Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吧  好好学着\N{\fs14\b0}Give me that, watch and learn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天得晚点回来了\N{\fs14\b0}So, um, I'm gonna be home late tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫什么\N{\fs14\b0}What's his name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如你先告诉我  你昨晚去见谁了\N{\fs14\b0}How about you tell me who you were meeting with last night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我估计你也不会说\N{\fs14\b0}Okay, I didn't think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是提前跟你打个招呼\N{\fs14\b0}I'm just, uh, giving you the heads-up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我让爸来看孩子了\N{\fs14\b0}'cause Dad's gonna babysit,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免得你不想看见他\N{\fs14\b0}in case you wanted to be somewhere else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事\N{\fs14\b0}We'll be fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来点\N{\fs14\b0}A bit more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在匡蒂科就是学这些的吗\N{\fs14\b0}Is that what they teach you in Quantico?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给我做一份吧\N{\fs14\b0}Now you can make me one, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上班要迟到了\N{\fs14\b0}I'm late for work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己做吧\N{\fs14\b0}Make it yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死人了你\N{\fs14\b0}You are so mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们\N{\fs14\b0}Yo, buddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs14\b0}You okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷路了你\N{\fs14\b0}You lost?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那个军事基地上班吗\N{\fs14\b0}You-- you work down the base there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我载你一程吧\N{\fs14\b0}Let me give you a ride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午好\N{\fs14\b0}Morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想为昨晚的事道歉\N{\fs14\b0}I want to say sorry about last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该告诉你我来不了的\N{\fs14\b0}I should've told you that I wasn't coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个...\N{\fs14\b0}The two of us...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太纠缠不清了\N{\fs14\b0}it's too complicated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14\b0}Right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想这么说来着\N{\fs14\b0}I was gonna say the same thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我很高兴我们想到一起去了\N{\fs14\b0}Okay, I'm glad we're on the same page.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不想把关系弄得太尴尬\N{\fs14\b0}I don't-- I don't want things to be awkward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  当然不会\N{\fs14\b0}No, of course not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}贝克堡军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么事吗\N{\fs14\b0}Can I help you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我在前面半英里处发现了这孩子\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, I picked up this kid about a half mile back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有空降兵纹身\N{\fs14\b0}He's got an airborne tat,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得他脑袋好像出了点问题\N{\fs14\b0}but, uh, I don't think he's right in the head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能过去看看吗\N{\fs14\b0}You think you guys could check him out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请下车\N{\fs14\b0}Can you step out of the car, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字  士兵\N{\fs14\b0}What's your name, soldier?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-过来  -不\N{\fs14\b0}- Come on. - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你不能带走我\N{\fs14\b0}No, you can't take me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我们是来帮你的\N{\fs14\b0}It's okay, we're here to help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能这么对我们  住手\N{\fs14\b0}You can't do this to us, stop!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱动  小子\N{\fs14\b0}Stay where you are, son!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三名受害者被宣告死亡\N{\fs14\b0}Three of the victims were declared dead,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一人正在医院抢救\N{\fs14\b0}one is in the hospital,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪手仍然逍遥法外\N{\fs14\b0}and the shooter is still on the loose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身份确认了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do we have an ID?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆军中士查理·纳比尔\N{\fs14\b0}Army Sergeant Charlie Napier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三次驻军伊拉克  胸前挂满了勋章\N{\fs14\b0}Three tours in Iraq, jacket full of medals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}查理·纳比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况通常在宪宾队的管辖范围之内\N{\fs14\b0}This is usually Military Police jurisdiction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  这些字母碎片\N{\fs14\b0}I know... these are letter fragments{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于简的左腿后侧\N{\fs14\b0}that are on the back of Jane's left leg{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们被四等分并加以旋转\N{\fs14\b0}that are divided into quarters and then rotated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像散落在桌子上的一箱子拼图碎片\N{\fs14\b0}It's like a box of puzzle pieces scattered on a table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你把它们拼凑起来...\N{\fs14\b0}When you fit them together...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}中士\N查理·纳比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早就破解了这条信息\N{\fs14\b0}We decoded this one already.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是当我的团队调查过之后\N{\fs14\b0}But when my team looked into it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现这是条死胡同\N{\fs14\b0}it was a dead end.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向他问过话吗\N{\fs14\b0}Did we question him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没法问  -为什么\N{\fs14\b0}- We couldn't. - Why not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为查理·纳比尔早在十八个月前就死了\N{\fs14\b0}Because Charlie Napier died 18 months ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伊拉克的一次行动中  死于土制炸弹爆炸\N{\fs14\b0}Killed in action, an IED explosion in Iraq.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个死人怎么能在军事基地开枪\N{\fs14\b0}How's a dead man shoot up a military base?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是  他的下一个目标是谁\N{\fs14\b0}And, more importantly, what's he gonna shoot up next?{\r}
