Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs18\c&HE1D9D6&\alpha10\fad(530,0)\t(23,2736,\fscx110\fscy110)\b0\pos(194,156)}第一季  第十二集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还知道关于这家伙的其它信息吗\N{\fs14\b0}What else do we know about this guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队模范\N{\fs14\b0}Army poster child,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中时就应征入伍\N{\fs14\b0}enlisted straight out of high school,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把每一分钱都寄回家\N{\fs14\b0}sent every penny home{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮他的单亲母亲维持生计\N{\fs14\b0}to a single mother to help pay the bills.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能确定这是同一个人吗\N{\fs14\b0}Are we sure it's the same guy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经将这个视频跟我们手上的所有\N{\fs14\b0}I've run this video through every biometric{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生物识别扫描信息一一比对过了\N{\fs14\b0}recognition scan we've got.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面部  声音  耳朵  是他没错\N{\fs14\b0}Face, voice, ear-- it's him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵  真的吗\N{\fs14\b0}Ear, really?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵包含很多重要信息\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, the ear's a treasure trove.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能从耳朵挖掘出的信息说出来能吓到你\N{\fs14\b0}You don't even want to know what I can do with an ear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是弄错了  还是有人想掩盖什么\N{\fs14\b0}Was this a screw-up or a cover-up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个炸弹爆炸的威力非常可怕\N{\fs14\b0}The IED explosion was pretty gruesome,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们没办法找全四分五裂的尸体\N{\fs14\b0}so they weren't able to recover a body.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们通过查理的牙齿和组织确认了身份\N{\fs14\b0}But they ID'd Charlie off of dental and tissue samples.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来某间实验室完全判断错误了\N{\fs14\b0}So some lab made a terrible mistake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者就是有人想让他消失\N{\fs14\b0}Or someone really wanted him off the grid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是什么\N{\fs14\b0}Hey, what are those?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多的名字\N{\fs14\b0}More names.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他四位士兵  全部遭受过不同的袭击\N{\fs14\b0}Four other soldiers, all different attacks,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部阵亡  就像查理一样\N{\fs14\b0}all KIA, just like Charlie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然查理还活着\N{\fs14\b0}So if Charlie's alive,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这些士兵也有可能还活着\N{\fs14\b0}then these other soldiers could be, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理说过"你不能这么对我们"\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie said, "You can't do this to us."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能还有其他同伴\N{\fs14\b0}He could be a part of a cell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说接下来恐怕会出现更多袭击事件\N{\fs14\b0}Which means there could be more attacks coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么要跟他曾经守卫的人民反目\N{\fs14\b0}Why would he turn against his own people like that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个人仇恨  不满体制  创伤应激障碍\N{\fs14\b0}Personal vendetta, institutional grudge, PTSD?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的档案里没有列出任何\N{\fs14\b0}His file didn't list any history{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反人类或者精神病病史\N{\fs14\b0}of insubordination or mental illness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  他的档案还注明他已死亡呢\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, but his file also listed him as dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fs14\b0}Hang on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理刚才用那辆卡车司机的手机\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie just used the truck driver's cell phone{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拨打了一个已停机的号码\N{\fs14\b0}to call an out-of-service landline.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他儿时的故居\N{\fs14\b0}It's his childhood home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他母亲现在还住在那里吗\N{\fs14\b0}Does his mother still live there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  她最近搬到北部去了\N{\fs14\b0}No, she moved upstate recently.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但要是他真的消失了很久\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, but if he was off the grid,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不会知道的\N{\fs14\b0}he wouldn't know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他是在找藏身之处吗\N{\fs14\b0}You think he was looking for someplace to lay low?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道只有一个办法\N{\fs14\b0}One way to find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧\N{\fs14\b0}Let's move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  拜托  帮帮我  他有枪\N{\fs14\b0}Please, please, help! He has a gun!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士  请到车后躲避一下\N{\fs14\b0}All right, ma'am, get behind that car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那儿\N{\fs14\b0}You stay there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德  萨帕塔  从房子后面包抄\N{\fs14\b0}Reade, Zapata, go around the back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和简从前门进去\N{\fs14\b0}Me and Jane will go through the front.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是联调局的  放下武器\N{\fs14\b0}This is the FBI. Drop the weapon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪在地上\N{\fs14\b0}Get down on your knees.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈在哪\N{\fs14\b0}Where's my mom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对她干了什么\N{\fs14\b0}What did you do with her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器  跪在地上\N{\fs14\b0}Drop the weapon and get down on your knees.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fs14\b0}Now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的撑不下去了\N{\fs14\b0}I can't take it anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撑不下去了\N{\fs14\b0}I can't take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们撑不下去了  就去那边敲钟\N{\fs14\b0}If you can't take it, then ring that bell!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进  前进  前进\N{\fs14\b0}Let's go, let's go, let's go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你速度得快点\N{\fs14\b0}You're gonna have to move faster!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你待的地方  小公主\N{\fs14\b0}You don't belong here, princess!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  摇铃吧\N{\fs14\b0}Let's go, ring it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆摇铃退出得了\N{\fs14\b0}Ring that damn bell and quit!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  放下武器  跪在地上\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie, put down the weapon and get down on your knees.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  我不能回去\N{\fs14\b0}Please... I can't go back there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想回去\N{\fs14\b0}I won't go back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回哪去\N{\fs14\b0}Go back where?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想见我妈\N{\fs14\b0}I just want my mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在这  查理\N{\fs14\b0}She's here, Charlie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈就在楼下\N{\fs14\b0}Your mom's downstairs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想和你聊聊  好吗\N{\fs14\b0}She wants to talk to you, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以把枪放下\N{\fs14\b0}So just put the gun down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们去告诉她你一切都好\N{\fs14\b0}and let's go tell her that you're okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs14\b0}All right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在等你  查理\N{\fs14\b0}She's waiting for you, Charlie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们下楼\N{\fs14\b0}Let's go down there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs14\b0}It's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-妈  不  放开我  -过来\N{\fs14\b0}- Mama! No, no! - Come here, come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs14\b0}No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  我不记得\N{\fs14\b0}I told you, I don't remember.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得你过去一年半\N{\fs14\b0}You don't remember where you've been{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪里吗\N{\fs14\b0}for the last year and a half?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs14\b0}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得的最后一件事是什么\N{\fs14\b0}What's the last thing you do remember?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个地牢\N{\fs14\b0}A dungeon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰\N{\fs14\b0}Flames.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地牢在哪\N{\fs14\b0}And where was this dungeon?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  你当时在哪\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie, where were you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在地狱\N{\fs14\b0}I was in hell...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被恶魔折磨\N{\fs14\b0}being tortured by the devil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔长什么样\N{\fs14\b0}What did this devil look like?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要和你说话\N{\fs14\b0}I'm not talking to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了我\N{\fs14\b0}You lied to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须得想起来  查理\N{\fs14\b0}You have to try to remember, Charlie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时你身边有谁\N{\fs14\b0}Who was there with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱是什么样子\N{\fs14\b0}What did hell look like?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么出来的\N{\fs14\b0}How'd you get out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我游过了一条河\N{\fs14\b0}I swam across a river.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么河\N{\fs14\b0}What river?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥河\N{\fs14\b0}The River Styx.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化验显示查理体内有氨基丙苯\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie's tested positive for amphetamines,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋剂  类固醇和麻醉剂\N{\fs14\b0}stimulates, steroids, and anesthetics.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使很小的剂量\N{\fs14\b0}Even in low doses,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些药物结合起来会致人衰弱\N{\fs14\b0}the combination of these drugs is massively debilitating.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而查理体内的含量惊人\N{\fs14\b0}And Charlie's levels are off the charts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就解释了他的行为\N{\fs14\b0}Well, that would explain his behavior.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但引起我注意的不是药的剂量\N{\fs14\b0}But it's not the volume that caught my eye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一剂药物就是泽塔互作蛋白\N{\fs14\b0}One of the drugs used was Zeta Interacting Protein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}泽塔互作蛋白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  这好像\N{\fs14\b0}Wait, like--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  就是用来清除你记忆的药物\N{\fs14\b0}Yes, exactly the same drug that was used to erase your memory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}泽塔互作蛋白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理体内含有过量复杂合成物\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie's body was overloaded with very complix composite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中就有泽塔互作蛋白\N{\fs14\b0}And ZIP was part of it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs14\b0}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这其中定有联系\N{\fs14\b0}So there's got to be a connection.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽塔互作蛋白不罕见  但你的事之前\N{\fs14\b0}Well, ZIP isn't a rare drug, but until your case,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没见过剂量这么高的\N{\fs14\b0}I'd never seen it used in such high doses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们的剂量一样吗\N{\fs14\b0}So are the levels similar here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不一样高  但差不多\N{\fs14\b0}Well, not quite as high, but close.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以对查理做出这些的\N{\fs14\b0}So the people that did this to Charlie{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能和简的是同一批人\N{\fs14\b0}could be the same people that did this to Jane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对自己做了这些\N{\fs14\b0}You did this to yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你对自己做了这些\N{\fs14\b0}You... did this... to yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是  但也有可能\N{\fs14\b0}Maybe, but there's also a possibility{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和她一点关联也没有\N{\fs14\b0}this might have nothing to do with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者和她大有关联\N{\fs14\b0}Or it could have everything to do with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们得找到这些人\N{\fs14\b0}So we got to find these people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的药物呢\N{\fs14\b0}What about these other drugs?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生可以出于合理医用目的开这些药吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do they have any legitimate medical purpose?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独开的话  可以\N{\fs14\b0}Individually, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这种组合和剂量\N{\fs14\b0}But with this combination and quantity,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}查理·纳比尔  药物化验分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上会导致病人昏迷不醒\N{\fs14\b0}most patients would be comatose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么查理没有\N{\fs14\b0}So why not Charlie?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我的疑惑之处\N{\fs14\b0}Well, that's what's been baffling me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的肾上腺素是正常水平的十倍\N{\fs14\b0}His epinephrine levels are 10 times the normal limit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交感神经系统极度兴奋\N{\fs14\b0}His entire sympathetic system is surging.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的心率和血压都失衡了\N{\fs14\b0}His heart rate, blood pressure, they're out of control.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,类固醇用来提升体能\N{\fs14\b0}Steroids to improve physical performance,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻黄素用来提高精神敏锐度\N{\fs14\b0}ephedrine to sharpen mental acuity,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及改变情绪的药物来抑制恐惧\N{\fs14\b0}and mood-altering drugs to dampen fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人一直处于应激状态\N{\fs14\b0}This guy is in a constant state of fight-or-flight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想创造出更"优秀"的士兵\N{\fs14\b0}Someone's trying to build a better soldier.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们军方曾做过这样的事\N{\fs14\b0}Our military has a history with this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把不知情的士兵当小白鼠\N{\fs14\b0}using unwitting soldiers to test everything{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从致幻剂到生化武器都试了个遍\N{\fs14\b0}from LSD to chemical weapons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果查理当时在他们那\N{\fs14\b0}If they got Charlie,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他四个士兵可能也在\N{\fs14\b0}they could have the four other soldiers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但我们怎么找到他们\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, but how do we find them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真是军事行动\N{\fs14\b0}If it is a military operation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五角大楼也不会轻易告诉我们在哪的\N{\fs14\b0}the Pentagon isn't just gonna tell us where they are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们的证人也算不上个可靠情报源\N{\fs14\b0}And our witness isn't exactly a font of information.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理体内泽塔互作蛋白的含量没有简的高\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie's ZIP levels aren't as high as Jane's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能在几周之内逐渐恢复记忆\N{\fs14\b0}He can start recovering memories within a few weeks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等不了那么久\N{\fs14\b0}We can't afford to wait that long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到熟悉的场景会触发记忆\N{\fs14\b0}Familiar sights trigger memories for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理想见他妈妈\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie wants his mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能把她带来\N{\fs14\b0}If we could get her here,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他会想起更多事情\N{\fs14\b0}maybe more memories would come back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能会记起来他被关在了哪里\N{\fs14\b0}He might remember where he was being held{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到查理的母亲\N{\fs14\b0}Let's track down Charlie's mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是你\N{\fs14\b0}It is you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟我说你死了\N{\fs14\b0}They told me you were dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fs14\b0}Baby...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我以为我失去你了\N{\fs14\b0}I-- I thought I lost you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  对不起\N{\fs14\b0}Mom, I-I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每夜都为你祈祷\N{\fs14\b0}I prayed for you every night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  你去哪了\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, Charlie... Where did you go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了地狱  但我逃出来了\N{\fs14\b0}I was in hell, but I got out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了上帝\N{\fs14\b0}I saw the face of God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  他叫我回家  回到你身边\N{\fs14\b0}Mom, he told me to go home to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她儿子杀了三个人\N{\fs14\b0}Her son killed three people{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她想做的只是拥抱他\N{\fs14\b0}and all she wants to do is hug him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回到她身边了\N{\fs14\b0}She got him back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对她来说足够了\N{\fs14\b0}It's all she cares about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还不肯原谅你父亲\N{\fs14\b0}Why haven't you forgiven your father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他没有...\N{\fs14\b0}You know he didn't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上的事是你误会了\N{\fs14\b0}that you were wrong about that night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情比你想的要复杂\N{\fs14\b0}It's more complicated than that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是这么说  那...\N{\fs14\b0}You always say that, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  有什么复杂的\N{\fs14\b0}Why? What's so complicated?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾是个糟糕的父亲\N{\fs14\b0}He was a terrible father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不闻不问  日夜酗酒\N{\fs14\b0}He was distant. He was drunk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我误会了一晚的事也不能改变这一切\N{\fs14\b0}Me being wrong about one night doesn't change any of that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他病了  不是吗\N{\fs14\b0}But he's sick, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纹身上列出的其他士兵的情况有进展了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Any progress on the other soldiers listed on the tattoo?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没\N{\fs14\b0}Uh, nothing yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我交叉对比了他们在哪训练\N{\fs14\b0}I cross-referenced where they trained,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪服役  和在哪长大的信息\N{\fs14\b0}where they served, where they grew up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续挖掘\N{\fs14\b0}Keep digging.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在查理身上做实验的人\N{\fs14\b0}Whoever was experimenting on Charlie{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能对其他四人也做了相同的实验\N{\fs14\b0}is probably doing the same to the other four.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须找到他们\N{\fs14\b0}We have to track them down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说找到谋害大卫的凶手后\N{\fs14\b0}You said you were gonna take a leave of absence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就打算申请探员休假的\N{\fs14\b0}after we found David's killer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我是打算的\N{\fs14\b0}I know, I was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但后来发生了泛亚921的那事\N{\fs14\b0}But then there was the whole Pan-Asian 921 thing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着又这件\N{\fs14\b0}and then this...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就感觉这里的事更为重要\N{\fs14\b0}Things here just feel more important.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是过来人\N{\fs14\b0}I've been where you are,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时的处理方式也跟你一模一样\N{\fs14\b0}and I dealt with it in the exact same way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起过一阵子的作用\N{\fs14\b0}And it worked for a while.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃避得越久\N{\fs14\b0}The longer you run from this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到逃不掉的那天它就伤你越深\N{\fs14\b0}the more it will hurt when it catches you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  你逃不掉的\N{\fs14\b0}And, trust me, it will catch you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得继续工作了\N{\fs14\b0}I should get back to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\fs14\b0}Let me go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你别让他们带走我\N{\fs14\b0}Please, don't let them take me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs14\b0}What the hell is going on?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是刑事调查局的人  说归他们管\N{\fs14\b0}They're CID claiming that they have jurisdiction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别探员肯恩·索普\N{\fs14\b0}Special Agent Ken Thorpe,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆军刑事调查司令部\N{\fs14\b0}Army Criminal Investigation Command,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本来就归我们管\N{\fs14\b0}and we do have jurisdiction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们调查还没结束\N{\fs14\b0}We're in the middle of an investigation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他触犯了联邦罪行\N{\fs14\b0}He committed a federal crime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在陆军管辖范围\N{\fs14\b0}On Army land.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者是陆军  他也是陆军\N{\fs14\b0}The victims were Army, he's Army.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的人别插手\N{\fs14\b0}You and your team need to stand down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有理由认为那个男人遭受了\N{\fs14\b0}We have reasons to believe that that man has been subjected{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非人道的医学试验\N{\fs14\b0}to inhumane medical experiments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前陆军宣告他死了\N{\fs14\b0}After the Army had declared him dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你能理解为什么我们不太愿意\N{\fs14\b0}So you can understand why we're reluctant{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他交给你们了吧\N{\fs14\b0}to hand him back to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对那一无所知\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know anything about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道就会告诉我们了吗\N{\fs14\b0}And you'd say if you did, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打给你上司\N{\fs14\b0}Call your boss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打给我上司  就算打给总统\N{\fs14\b0}Call my boss. Hell, call the president.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都会跟你说同样的话\N{\fs14\b0}They'll all tell you the same thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的案子\N{\fs14\b0}This is my case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们走\N{\fs14\b0}Let them go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就任由他这么做吗\N{\fs14\b0}You're just gonna let this happen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-退下  -求你别让他们把我带回那里\N{\fs14\b0}- Stand down. - Don't let them take me back there... please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事能把简纹身上的所有士兵联系起来\N{\fs14\b0}I found something linking all the soldiers on Jane's tattoo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们互相认识吗\N{\fs14\b0}Did they know each other?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们活着的时候不认识\N{\fs14\b0}Not while they were alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五人都是被声称在土制炸弹爆炸中身亡\N{\fs14\b0}All five were declared dead in IED attacks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且每起爆炸案\N{\fs14\b0}And in every case,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一支到达现场的急救队\N{\fs14\b0}the first responders on the scene{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都来自同一家私人军事承包商\N{\fs14\b0}were the same private military contractor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪家\N{\fs14\b0}Who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯莱克\N{\fs14\b0}Northlake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么久才发现这层关系\N{\fs14\b0}Why'd it take this long to make that connection?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种承包商一般都不喜欢曝光\N{\fs14\b0}Contractors like this go out of their way to be opaque.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每支急救队都是由不同机构资助的\N{\fs14\b0}Each of the responders were paid by separate entities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但全都受诺斯莱克控制  对吗\N{\fs14\b0}But Northlake controls all of them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们掩盖得非常好  但的确是这样\N{\fs14\b0}They make it very hard to uncover, but yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军方医疗人员得好几个小时\N{\fs14\b0}It could've taken hours for the military M.Es{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能赶到袭击现场\N{\fs14\b0}to arrive at the attack site.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯莱克有充分的时间处理那些尸体\N{\fs14\b0}Northlake would've had access to those bodies the entire time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以诺斯莱克绑架了这些军人\N{\fs14\b0}So Northlake kidnapped these soldiers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造他们死亡的假象\N{\fs14\b0}faked their deaths.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正在进行这些实验的其实是他们\N{\fs14\b0}They're the ones responsible for running these experiments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以说得通\N{\fs14\b0}Well, it makes sense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人军事承包商存在动机\N{\fs14\b0}Private military contractors have the motive{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在为雇佣兵开发这些药品\N{\fs14\b0}to develop these drugs for the mercenaries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一群没有道德良知的人\N{\fs14\b0}Not the most morally scrupulous, either.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发\N{\fs14\b0}Let's move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\fs14\b0}Leave me alone!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁  你们想干什么\N{\fs14\b0}Who are you? What do you want from me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有刑事调查局的探员都当场死亡\N{\fs14\b0}All the CID agents were dead on the scene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理呢\N{\fs14\b0}What about Charlie?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他失踪了\N{\fs14\b0}He's missing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次精准的军事化协同攻击\N{\fs14\b0}This attack was coordinated, military-style precision,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是诺斯莱克的行事风格\N{\fs14\b0}definitely Northlake's M.O.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会杀了他吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you think they'll kill him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fs14\b0}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有理由让他活着\N{\fs14\b0}They wanted him alive for a reason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最大的希望就是找到\N{\fs14\b0}Our best bet is to track down{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们进行这些实验的地方\N{\fs14\b0}where they've been conducting these experiments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有查到他被关在哪里\N{\fs14\b0}Do we know anything yet about where he was being held,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了"地狱"之外\N{\fs14\b0}outside of "Hell"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个司机让查理搭车\N{\fs14\b0}That driver that picked up Charlie,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时是在哪\N{\fs14\b0}where was that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上八点  在贝克堡基地前的路上\N{\fs14\b0}Down the road from Fort Beck at about 8:00 a.m.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即定位\N{\fs14\b0}Drop a pin in it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博登的毒理报告不是缩小了\N{\fs14\b0}Didn't Borden's toxicology report{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}贝克堡\N军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理最后一次被下药的时间范围吗\N{\fs14\b0}narrow down the last time Charlie was drugged?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  在早上七点半左右\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, at around 7:30 a.m.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  所以他大概跑了半小时\N{\fs14\b0}All right, so he's been on the run for half an hour,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多跑了六到八公里\N{\fs14\b0}could've covered four to five miles at most.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}贝克堡\N军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理不是说他逃出来之后\N{\fs14\b0}Didn't Charlie say he swam across the River Styx{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游过了冥河吗\N{\fs14\b0}after he escaped?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被药物搞得神志不清了\N{\fs14\b0}He was drugged out of his mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但是如果他其实游过了其他东西呢\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, but what if he swam across something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说一条真的河\N{\fs14\b0}A real river.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}贝克堡\N军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有帮助\N{\fs14\b0}Well, that helps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范围还是很大\N{\fs14\b0}It's still a lot of ground to cover.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听这个\N{\fs14\b0}Hey, here's something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初步报告显示\N{\fs14\b0}So the preliminary reports say,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击查理押运车的其中一个枪手\N{\fs14\b0}one of the gunman who attacked Charlie's transport{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了一个带有油性残留的脚印\N{\fs14\b0}left a boot print with oil residue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六号燃油\N{\fs14\b0}Heating oil number six,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约从2010年就开始淘汰这种油了\N{\fs14\b0}which New York started phasing out in 2010.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们关押他的地方\N{\fs14\b0}Wherever they held him,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有一个那种燃油的锅炉\N{\fs14\b0}they must've had one of those boilers there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印证了他看到的火焰\N{\fs14\b0}The flames he saw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少建筑还在用那种燃油\N{\fs14\b0}How many buildings still use that heating oil?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据环保署的记录\N{\fs14\b0}According to EPA records,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这范围内  只有五栋\N{\fs14\b0}in our radius, it's just five.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足够我们查下去了\N{\fs14\b0}It's enough to go on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  我还以为见不到你了\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie, I thought we lost you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  我们很快就会离开这里\N{\fs14\b0}Don't worry, we're leaving here soon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切很快就会结束了\N{\fs14\b0}It'll all be over before you know it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们那五栋楼里的第一栋\N{\fs14\b0}First of our five buildings{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在三公里之后出现\N{\fs14\b0}should be coming up in half a mile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么知道要哪栋\N{\fs14\b0}How will we know what to look for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法  我们得一栋一栋的找\N{\fs14\b0}We won't... we have to clear them one by one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}附近地标
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  查理说他出来的时候\N{\fs14\b0}Wait, Charlie said he saw the face of God{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了上帝之脸\N{\fs14\b0}when he came out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按一下语音控制按钮\N{\fs14\b0}Hit the voice command button.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说出命令\N{\fs14\b0}Please say a command.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地  迪非逊大道912号\N{\fs14\b0}Destination, 912 Division Ave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝之脸在迪非逊大道912号\N{\fs14\b0}The face of God is at 912 Division?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这么说吧\N{\fs14\b0}Kinda.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝之脸\N{\fs14\b0}Face of God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  塔莎\N{\fs14\b0}Nice work, Tasha.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们要找的五栋楼之一\N{\fs14\b0}That's one of our five buildings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理出来的时候可以看到教堂\N{\fs14\b0}Charlie would've had a view of the church on his way out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发\N{\fs14\b0}Let's move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要拉响那个铃\N{\fs14\b0}You want to ring that bell,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗  公主\N{\fs14\b0}don't you, princess?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都知道你想放弃\N{\fs14\b0}We all know you want to quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\b0}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都知道你会放弃\N{\fs14\b0}We all know you gonna quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别再浪费我们的时间\N{\fs14\b0}So quit wasting our time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去把那该死的铃拉响\N{\fs14\b0}and ring that damn bell!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简\N{\fs14\b0}Jane?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个死了\N{\fs14\b0}This one's dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是\N{\fs14\b0}Same here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四名士兵  五张床\N{\fs14\b0}Four soldiers. Five beds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理还在他们手上\N{\fs14\b0}They still have Charlie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺斯莱克一定意识到情况危险了\N{\fs14\b0}Northlake must've figured the heat was on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们匆匆离开了这里\N{\fs14\b0}They left this place in a hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还销毁了所有证据\N{\fs14\b0}And destroyed all the evidence behind them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有全部销毁\N{\fs14\b0}They didn't destroy everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从其中一个损坏的硬盘里\N{\fs14\b0}I recovered a partial video file{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复了一段视频文件\N{\fs14\b0}off one of the damaged hard drives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为删除文件就能防止...\N{\fs14\b0}They thought deleting them would stop them from--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.40,0:24:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想销毁硬盘\N{\fs14\b0}If you want to destroy a hard drive,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用高能磁铁或者...\N{\fs14\b0}use a high-powered magnet or--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你发现了什么\N{\fs14\b0}All right, what'd you find?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,42号试验  实验对象三\N{\fs14\b0}Trial 42, subject three,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主测试人斯派西诺博士\N{\fs14\b0}Dr. Sparacino principal examiner.{\r}
