Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.97,0:33:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆军刑事调查局有审判权\N{\fs14\b0}Army CID had jurisdiction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.25,0:33:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也无能为力\N{\fs14\b0}It was out of my hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们没放他走  他现在可能还活着\N{\fs14\b0}If we hadn't let him go, he might still be alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.88,0:33:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干我们这一行\N{\fs14\b0}In this job,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.17,0:33:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须要接受一些你无法认同的决定\N{\fs14\b0}we all have to accept decisions that we don't agree with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.71,0:33:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做指挥机制\N{\fs14\b0}It's called chain of command.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士  他们在楼上等你了\N{\fs14\b0}Ma'am, they're ready for you upstairs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.47,0:33:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还想继续在这个团队里待下去\N{\fs14\b0}And if you are gonna remain part of this team,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:34:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须学会跟着团队的步调行事\N{\fs14\b0}you're gonna have to learn to function as part of a unit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Are we clear?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.00,0:34:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你并不是他们中的一员\N{\fs14\b0}You know that you're not one of them...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.47,0:34:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是这个庞大机构中的一颗螺丝钉\N{\fs14\b0}that you're just a cog in their machine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很美味\N{\fs14\b0}Looks delicious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.92,0:34:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝起来更棒\N{\fs14\b0}Tastes even better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:34:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉说喝这个东西\N{\fs14\b0}Sarah says it's supposed to be good{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.25,0:35:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的血小板什么的有好处\N{\fs14\b0}for my platelets or something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.56,0:35:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说  这就像用玩具枪跟坦克斗一样\N{\fs14\b0}You ask me, it's like trying to stop a tank with a BB gun, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.22,0:35:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你也了解你妹妹\N{\fs14\b0}you know your sister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.68,0:35:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我帮把手吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you want a hand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.28,0:35:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉最近交往的那个人  你知道多少\N{\fs14\b0}Do you know anything about this guy Sarah's out with?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.21,0:35:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不想告诉我那个人的名字\N{\fs14\b0}Just that she won't tell me his name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.99,0:35:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是来真的了\N{\fs14\b0}Must be serious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.14,0:35:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs14\b0}Sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.61,0:35:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你看起来美极了  -谢谢\N{\fs14\b0}- You look amazing. - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.44,0:35:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服务员戴的耳环比我的车还贵\N{\fs14\b0}The waitress's earrings cost more than my car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管她戴了什么耳环  我喜欢你的车\N{\fs14\b0}Never mind her earrings, I like your car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.66,0:35:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是辆古董车\N{\fs14\b0}It's-- it's an antique.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.77,0:35:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我点了你爱喝的甜饮料\N{\fs14\b0}I got you your usual sugar drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.92,0:36:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\b0}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.66,0:36:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\fs14\b0}Cheers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.90,0:36:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直接说了\N{\fs14\b0}Okay, I'm just gonna come right out and say it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.46,0:36:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想你\N{\fs14\b0}I missed you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.73,0:36:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两天前才见过面\N{\fs14\b0}I saw you two days ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.65,0:36:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天前见的我就不能想你吗\N{\fs14\b0}I can't miss you after two days?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.83,0:36:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了  我还挺招人惦记的\N{\fs14\b0}Well, you sure can, I am pretty "miss-able."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.81,0:36:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸怎么了\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, no, what happened to your face?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.95,0:36:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很糟  实际没那么严重\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, it probably looks worse than what it really is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.64,0:36:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fs14\b0}I'm-- I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.67,0:36:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉我哥哥的时候他打的  对不对\N{\fs14\b0}My brother hit you when you told him, didn't he?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.75,0:36:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是工作时候伤的  不过不是他打的\N{\fs14\b0}Well, it is from work, but, no, he didn't hit me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.33,0:36:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没告诉他\N{\fs14\b0}I didn't tell him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.84,0:36:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你个胆小鬼  -我知道\N{\fs14\b0}- You wimp. - I know, I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.43,0:36:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟你哥哥说的\N{\fs14\b0}I-I-I'll speak to your brother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.97,0:36:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是  想等到他没那么大压力的时候说\N{\fs14\b0}I just... trying to wait until he's not so stressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.96,0:36:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道  -那永远等不到了\N{\fs14\b0}- You know. - So never.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.68,0:36:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我来说吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you want me to do it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.81,0:36:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  那样...听着\N{\fs14\b0}No, no, no, that's... look...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.55,0:36:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要由我来说\N{\fs14\b0}it has to come from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.59,0:36:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想确保能把话说清楚\N{\fs14\b0}I just want to make sure I do it right, you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.11,0:37:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开了三天车\N{\fs14\b0}Well, three-- three days we drove.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.80,0:37:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买那些票花了我一大笔钱\N{\fs14\b0}I paid a fortune for those tickets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.60,0:37:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妹妹一看到那个打扮成\N{\fs14\b0}And the second your sister saw that guy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.56,0:37:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁托{\fs14}[米老鼠的忠犬]{\c}的人就激动哭了\N{\fs14\b0}in the-- in the Pluto costume, she burst into tears!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.74,0:37:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱没白花\N{\fs14\b0}Money well spent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.59,0:37:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上究竟发生了什么\N{\fs14\b0}What really happened that night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.60,0:37:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰勒失踪那晚\N{\fs14\b0}The night that Taylor disappeared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.52,0:37:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fs14\b0}Where were you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.27,0:37:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你三小时前就离开了晚宴\N{\fs14\b0}You left that dinner party for three hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.99,0:37:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自告奋勇去买酒\N{\fs14\b0}I volunteered for a booze run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我忘了买酒的地方\N{\fs14\b0}I'd forgotten that the liquor stores--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.66,0:37:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多在周日不开门\N{\fs14\b0}most of them weren't open on Sundays.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.17,0:37:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日的确不开\N{\fs14\b0}Sundays, yeah, I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.46,0:37:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不得不开车去俄亥俄\N{\fs14\b0}So you had to drive halfway to Ohio.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.43,0:37:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我...\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, I--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.21,0:37:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听你骗了大家25年的谎话  爸爸\N{\fs14\b0}I don't want the line that you fed everyone for 25 years, Dad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.29,0:37:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是实情\N{\fs14\b0}That's the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.60,0:38:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的鞋上怎么都是泥\N{\fs14\b0}Why were your shoes muddy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.16,0:38:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我睡着了\N{\fs14\b0}You thought I was asleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.19,0:38:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我没有\N{\fs14\b0}I wasn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.96,0:38:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你到家后用水冲鞋\N{\fs14\b0}I saw you hosing off your shoes when you got home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.75,0:38:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有...\N{\fs14\b0}I didn't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.57,0:38:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还活着  科特\N{\fs14\b0}She's alive, Kurt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.15,0:38:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要隐瞒你去了哪儿\N{\fs14\b0}Then why did you lie about where you were?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.31,0:38:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我当时想自杀\N{\fs14\b0}Because I was trying to kill myself!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.45,0:38:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14\b0}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.38,0:38:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年我抑郁了很久\N{\fs14\b0}I was depressed for a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.08,0:38:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想过自杀  可我下不了决心\N{\fs14\b0}And I had thought about it before and I just couldn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.60,0:38:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我终于受够了\N{\fs14\b0}And finally, I'd just had enough,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.45,0:38:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开车去了萨斯奎哈纳河\N{\fs14\b0}and I drove to the Susquehanna,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.21,0:38:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走进了河里\N{\fs14\b0}and I walked... I walked in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.25,0:38:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这个情景一直挥之不去\N{\fs14\b0}And then I just couldn't shake this image.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.84,0:38:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情景\N{\fs14\b0}What image?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.45,0:39:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和莎拉在参加我的葬礼\N{\fs14\b0}You and Sarah... at my funeral.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.47,0:39:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会穿什么\N{\fs14\b0}What-- what you'd be wearing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.43,0:39:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在哪儿\N{\fs14\b0}where you'd be sitting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.79,0:39:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我回到了车上\N{\fs14\b0}So I just, uh... got back in the car{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.56,0:39:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开回了家\N{\fs14\b0}and drove home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.58,0:39:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以鞋上全是泥\N{\fs14\b0}With muddy shoes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.88,0:39:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs14\b0}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年了\N{\fs14\b0}After all these years...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.35,0:39:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉别人\N{\fs14\b0}why didn't you tell anyone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.75,0:39:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会相信我\N{\fs14\b0}Who was gonna believe me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.02,0:39:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  莎拉\N{\fs14\b0}Me! Sarah!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.96,0:39:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs14\b0}Mom!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.04,0:39:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到羞耻\N{\fs14\b0}I was so ashamed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.43,0:39:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点就...\N{\fs14\b0}I had almost...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且\N{\fs14\b0}And...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.84,0:39:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们和你们妈妈绝对理解不了\N{\fs14\b0}Your-- and your mother never would've understood me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.99,0:39:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正莎拉从没相信过流言\N{\fs14\b0}Sarah, she never believed what people said anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.18,0:39:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你  我希望你\N{\fs14\b0}But you, I wanted you--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.76,0:39:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能离我远远的\N{\fs14\b0}I wanted you as far away from me as I could get you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.43,0:39:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs14\b0}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.40,0:39:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是满腔怒火\N{\fs14\b0}I was so full of rage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.55,0:40:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是满腔...\N{\fs14\b0}I was so full of...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.67,0:40:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望你变得像我一样\N{\fs14\b0}And I didn't want you to turn out like me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.10,0:40:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  柯特\N{\fs14\b0}I'm so sorry, Kurt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.58,0:40:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fs14\b0}I'm-- I'm-- you know--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.84,0:40:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  柯特\N{\fs14\b0}I'm so sorry, Kurt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.78,0:40:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的...\N{\fs14\b0}I'm so...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.22,0:40:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\N{\fs14\b0}Good work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.43,0:40:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这是她的笔\N{\fs14\b0}How do you know it's hers?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.67,0:40:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果两支笔真的一模一样\N{\fs14\b0}If they were really the same--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.66,0:40:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\b0}I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.97,0:40:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我知道了你为什么会给我这个任务\N{\fs14\b0}And I know why you gave me this mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.23,0:40:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs14\b0}You do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.80,0:41:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想测试我的忠诚度  我合格了\N{\fs14\b0}It was a test of my loyalty, and I passed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.50,0:41:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信守了诺言  现在你欠我一些答案\N{\fs14\b0}I held up my end, and now you owe me some answers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.94,0:41:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个胡子大汉\N{\fs14\b0}The bearded man...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.52,0:41:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能相信他们\N{\fs14\b0}You can't trust them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.22,0:41:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们的人\N{\fs14\b0}Yes, he was with us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.79,0:41:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让我别相信"他们"\N{\fs14\b0}He told me not to trust "Them."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.40,0:41:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他指的是谁\N{\fs14\b0}Who did he mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.75,0:41:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局的人\N{\fs14\b0}The FBI.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.57,0:41:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁开枪打死他的\N{\fs14\b0}Why would-- who shot him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换个问题\N{\fs14\b0}Ask me another question.{\r}
